  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Use pure HTML + Tailwind for the marketing pages to allow for creative layouts, overlapping elements, and soft SVG wave dividers.",
    "Use Shadcn UI components heavily for the Admin Dashboard and the Appointment Booking Form, but customize them to fit the clean, light, elegant medical aesthetic.",
    "Install and use 'lucide-react' for all icons (e.g., teeth, sparkles, calendars, map pins).",
    "Install Google Fonts: 'Cormorant Garamond' (for headings) and 'Outfit' (for body text). Add them to your frontend/tailwind.config.js.",
    "Ensure all interactive elements have 'data-testid' attributes per the testing requirements.",
    "The admin dashboard should use a compact density, prioritizing data clarity over large typography. Use 'Outfit' font for the tables.",
    "Avoid cartoonish design elements. Keep the tone premium, trustworthy, and relaxing, matching a high-end coastal dental clinic.",
    "Ensure you extract and use the images from this JSON file for Hero, 7 Services, Dentist Portrait, 3 Testimonials, and Clinic Interior."
  ]
